Reason>>> Looks like Jon is volunteering :)

In all seriousness, the hard part will be tracking the
precise configuration of splits (the tree of vertical and
horizontals and the associated percentages) to deal with
shifting around between tabs. The lower-level
horizontal/vertical panels stuff is all there and easy.

